- Transaction routed to `ait-island1` mempool namespace, not `ait-hub`
- Transaction included in `ait-island1` block by `ait-island1` proposer
- Backward compat: tx without `chain_id` uses hub's default chain
- Gossip path still works (unchanged — already correct)
- Marketplace endpoint still works (unchanged — already correct)

